to":1328.8},{"content":"在最高層被救下了","from":1331.01,"location":2,"to":1335.48},{"content":"誕生在永恆的星球上","from":1335.61,"location":2,"to":1341.25},{"content":"背對著逐漸模糊的景色","from":1354.31,"location":2,"to":1358.6},{"content":"試著開始了生活","from":1358.65,"location":2,"to":1363.57},{"content":"收集 再失去","from":1363.58,"location":2,"to":1368.21},{"content":"打開身旁的窗戶","from":1368.44,"location":2,"to":1373.31},{"content":"「回憶增加了嗎?」","from":1373.48,"location":2,"to":1378.6},{"content":"不要死腦筋啦","from":1378.83,"location":2,"to":1381.69},{"content":"大膽走出來吧","from":1381.71,"location":2,"to":1384.2},{"content":"你會創造出來的","from":1384.7,"location":2,"to":1389.35},{"content":"最終觸碰的","from":1392.26,"location":2,"to":1397.32},{"content":"那個奇蹟","from":1397.58,"location":2,"to":1399.26},{"content":"我們來聊聊吧","from":1399.26,"location":2,"to":1402.15},{"content":"從未設想過的景色","from":1403.11,"location":2,"to":1407.94},{"content":"將填滿你的世界","from":1408.01,"location":2,"to":1413.41}]}